ng Pages\tNot Started\t0%\t-\t[Your Name]\tDesign Pages\t=HYPERLINK(\"#Landing\") Social Media\tNot Started\t0%\t-\t[Your Name]\tSchedule Posts\t=HYPERLINK(\"#Social\") Automation Formula Examples: Status: =IF(B2>0,\"In Progress\",IF(B2=100,\"Complete\",\"Not Started\")) Completion: Pulls from each sheet's completion tracker SHEET 2: 🏢 Brand Foundation Section\tInput Field\tYour Response\tAI Prompt Template\tExpected Output\tOutput Location\tStatus BRAND BASICS Brand Name\tEnter your brand name\t[Input]\t-\tBrand Name\tCopy to all sheets\t☐ Industry/Niche\tWhat industry?\t[Input]\t-\tIndustry Category\tProduct sheet\t☐ Mission Statement\tWhy does your brand exist?\t[Input]\t\"Create a compelling mission statement for [Brand] in [Industry] that [Purpose]\"\t1-2 sentence mission\tBrand Assets\t☐ Vision Statement\tWhere are you going?\t[Input]\t\"Create an inspiring vision statement for [Brand] that shows our 5-year goal in [Industry]\"\t1-2 sentence vision\tBrand Assets\t☐ BRAND VOICE Tone Adjectives\tPick 3-5 adjectives\t[Input: e.g., Professional, Innovative, Friendly]\t-\tVoice Guidelines\tAll content sheets\t☐ Communication Style\tFormal/Casual/Mixed\t[Dropdown]\t\"Create a brand voice guide for [Brand] with [Tone] that appeals to [Target Audience]\"\t200-word voice guide\tContent Strategy\t☐ BRAND POSITIONING Unique Value Prop\tWhat makes you different?\t[Input]\t\"Create 5 unique value propositions for [Brand] that differentiate from [Competitors] in [Market]\"\t5 UVP options\tProduct sheet\t☐ Target Market\tWho do you serve?\t[Input]\t-\tMarket Definition\tAvatar sheet\t☐ Price Position\tBudget/Mid/Premium/Luxury\t[Dropdown]\t-\tPricing Tier\tProduct sheet\t☐ BRAND STORY Founder Story\tYour background\t[Input]\t\"Transform this founder background into a compelling brand story: [Input]. Focus on the problem, journey, and mission.\"\t300-word story\tAbout Us content\t☐ Problem You Solve\tWhat pain point?\t[Input]\t-\tProblem Statement\tAll marketing\t☐ Solution Provided\tHow you solve it\t[Input]\t\"Create a clear, benefit-focused solution statement: We help [Avatar] achieve [Result] by [Method] so they can [Benefit]\"\tSolution Statement\tAll marketing\t☐ Column H: Automation Checkbox Column I: AI Generation Button (Apps Script trigger) SHEET 3: 📦 Product Definition Product Element\tInput Required\tYour Input\tAI Prompt\tGenerated Output\tUse In\tStatus CORE PRODUCT Product Name\tOfficial product name\t[Input]\t\"Generate 10 alternative product names for [Description] targeting [Avatar]. Style: [Brand Voice]\"\t10 name options\tAll materials\t☐ Product Type\tPhysical/Digital/Service/Course/Software\t[Dropdown]\t-\tProduct Category\tStrategy docs\t☐ Product Category\tSpecific category\t[Input]\t-\tCategory Tags\tSEO/Ads\t☐ PRODUCT DESCRIPTION Short Description\t1 sentence\t[Input]\t\"Create a compelling 1-sentence product description for [Product] that includes the main benefit for [Avatar]\"\tPower sentence\tAds, Social\t☐ Medium Description\t2-3 sentences\t[Auto-generated from AI]\t\"Expand into a 3-sentence description covering: What it is, Who it's for, Main transformation\"\t3-sentence pitch\tLanding pages\t☐ Long Description\tFull product detail\t[Auto-generated from AI]\t\"Create a detailed product description (300 words) covering: Features, Benefits, Transformation, Proof, CTA. For [Product] targeting [Avatar]\"\tFull description\tSales pages\t☐ FEATURES & BENEFITS Feature 1\tWhat it includes\t[Input]\t\"Convert this feature into a benefit statement: [Feature]\"\tBenefit statement\tSales copy\t☐ Feature 2\tWhat it includes\t[Input]\t\"Convert this feature into a benefit statement: [Feature]\"\tBenefit statement\tSales copy\t☐ Feature 3\tWhat it includes\t[Input]\t\"Convert this feature into a benefit statement: [Feature]\"\tBenefit statement\tSales copy\t☐ (Add more rows) PRICING Base Price\tStandard price\t[Input: $]\t-\tPrice Point\tAll sales materials\t☐ Payment Options\tOne-time/Subscription/Payment plan\t[Dropdown]\t\"Create 3 pricing presentation options for $[Price] that maximize perceived value for [Avatar]\"\t3 pricing frames\tSales pages\t☐ Discount Strategy\tAny promotions?\t[Input]\t\"Create a launch discount strategy for [Product] at $[Price] with urgency and scarcity elements\"\tPromo plan\tLaunch materials\t☐ TRANSFORMATION Before State\tWhere customer starts\t[Input]\t\"Create a vivid 'before state' description of [Avatar] struggling with [Problem]\"\tPain-focused narrative\tSales copy\t☐ After State\tWhere customer ends\t[Input]\t\"Create an aspirational 'after state' description of [Avatar] achieving [Result] after using [Product]\"\tBenefit-focused narrative\tSales copy\t☐ Time to Result\tHow long?\t[Input]\t-\tTimeline promise\tMarketing claims\t☐ PROOF & VALIDATION Social Proof Type\tTestimonials/Case studies/Stats\t[Dropdown]\t-\tProof Strategy\tTrust-building content\t☐ Guarantee\tWhat guarantee offered?\t[Input]\t\"Write a powerful, risk-reversal guarantee for [Product] that emphasizes [Benefit] and removes buyer hesitation\"\tGuarantee copy\tSales pages\t☐ SHEET 4: 👤 Avatar/ICP (Ideal Customer Profile) Avatar Element\tResearch Question\tYour Input\tAI Prompt\tGenerated Output\tUse Case\tComplete DEMOGRAPHICS Age Range\tPrimary age bracket\t[Input: e.g., 35-55]\t-\tAge targeting\tAd platforms\t☐ Gender\tPrimary gender\t[Dropdown: M/F/All]\t-\tGender targeting\tAd platforms\t☐ Income Level\tAnnual income range\t[Input: $]\t-\tEconomic profile\tPricing strategy\t☐ Location\tGeographic focus\t[Input]\t-\tGeo targeting\tAd platforms\t☐ Education Level\tTypical education\t[Input]\t-\tSophistication level\tContent complexity\t☐ Occupation\tJob titles/roles\t[Input]\t-\tProfessional targeting\tLinkedIn ads\t☐ PSYCHOGRAPHICS Values\tWhat do they care about?\t[Input]\t\"Based on these values [Input], create messaging angles that resonate emotionally with [Avatar]\"\t5 messaging angles\tAll content\t☐ Goals\tWhat are they trying to achieve?\t[Input]\t-\tAspiration targeting\tBenefit-focused copy\t☐ Fears\tWhat keeps them up at night?\t[Input]\t\"Transform these fears [Input] into empathetic problem-focused ad hooks (10 variations)\"\t10 pain-point hooks\tAd copy\t☐ Frustrations\tCurrent pain points\t[Input]\t\"Create 10 'agitate the pain' statements based on these frustrations: [Input]\"\t10 agitation statements\tSales copy\t☐ Desires\tUltimate outcome wanted\t[Input]\t\"Create 10 desire-focused headlines based on: [Input]\"\t10 benefit headlines\tHeadlines\t☐ BEHAVIORAL Online Behavior\tWhere do they hang out online?\t[Input]\t-\tPlatform strategy\tChannel selection\t☐ Content Preferences\tWhat content do they consume?\t[Input]\t\"Create a content strategy map for [Avatar] who consumes [Content Types]\"\tContent calendar themes\tContent sheet\t☐ Buying Triggers\tWhat makes them buy?\t[Input]\t\"Based on these buying triggers [Input], create 5 urgency-based offers\"\t5 offer frameworks\tPromotions\t☐ Objections\tWhy might they NOT buy?\t[Input]\t\"Create objection-handling scripts for these objections: [Input]\"\tObjection handlers\tSales copy/FAQs\t☐ AVATAR NARRATIVE Day in the Life\tDescribe their typical day\t[Input]\t\"Create a detailed 'day in the life' narrative for [Avatar Name] that shows where [Product] fits naturally\"\t400-word narrative\tEmpathy-based content\t☐ Avatar Name\tGive them a name\t[Input: e.g., \"Marketing Mary\"]\t-\tReference name\tAll documents\t☐ Avatar Photo\tDescription/URL\t[Input]\t-\tVisual reference\tPresentations\t☐ SHEET 5: 📝 Content Strategy & Calendar Date\tPlatform\tContent Type\tTopic/Theme\tHook/Headline\tAI Prompt Used\tGenerated Content\tStatus\tPerformance 11/18/25\tLinkedIn\tArticle\tProblem Awareness\t\"Are You Making This Mistake With [Topic]?\"\t\"Write a 500-word LinkedIn article about [Problem] for [Avatar]. Include: Hook, Problem agitation, Solution tease, CTA to [Product]\"\t[Generated text]\tDraft\t- 11/18/25\tInstagram\tCarousel\tProduct Education\t\"5 Ways [Product] Transforms [Result]\"\t\"Create a 10-slide carousel script about [Product benefits]. Each slide: Headline + 20 words. End with CTA.\"\t[Slide content]\tScheduled\t- 11/19/25\tYouTube\tVideo Script\tTutorial\t\"How to [Achieve Result] in 30 Days\"\t\"Write a 10-minute YouTube script: Intro hook, Problem, 5-step solution using [Product], Social proof, CTA\"\t[Script]\tTo Film\t- 11/19/25\tBlog\tSEO Article\tComparison\t\"[Product] vs [Competitor]: Honest Review\"\t\"Write a 1500-word comparison article optimized for '[Keyword]'. Include: Features, Pros/Cons, Pricing, Verdict favoring [Product]\"\t[Article]\tDraft\t- 11/20/25\tFacebook\tAd\tDirect Response\t\"Finally, A Solution For [Pain Point]\"\t\"Create 3 Facebook ad variations (125 words each) using PAS formula for [Product] targeting [Avatar]\"\t[3 ad copies]\tReady\t- Additional Columns: Content Pillar (dropdown: Education, Inspiration, Promotion, Entertainment) Funnel Stage (Awareness, Consideration, Conversion, Retention) CTA (What action do you want?) Visual Asset Link (Link to Canva/image) Publish Date/Time Engagement Metrics (Auto-pull if possible) SHEET 6: 🎯 Ad Campaign Manager Campaign\tPlatform\tObjective\tAudience\tBudget\tAd Format\tHeadline\tBody Copy\tCTA\tAI Prompt\tStatus\tROAS Launch Campaign 1\tFacebook\tConversions\t[Avatar] 35-55, USA\t$50/day\tSingle Image\t\"Stop Struggling With [Problem]\"\t[Generated copy]\t\"Get Started Now\"\t\"Write a Facebook ad using Problem-Agitate-Solution framework for [Product]. Target: [Avatar]. Include: Attention-grabbing hook, 3 pain points, Solution intro, Risk reversal, CTA\"\tActive\t3.2x Retargeting\tFacebook\tConversions\tWebsite visitors\t$30/day\tVideo\t\"Still Thinking About [Product]?\"\t[Generated copy]\t\"Claim 20% Off\"\t\"Write a retargeting ad for people who visited our site. Include: Acknowledgment, Social proof, Limited-time offer, Urgency, CTA\"\tActive\t4.5x Cold Traffic\tGoogle\tClicks\tSearch: [Keyword]\t$40/day\tSearch Ad\t\"[Product] - [Main Benefit]\"\t[Generated copy]\t\"Learn More\"\t\"Write 3 Google search ad headlines (30 char) and 2 descriptions (90 char) targeting keyword '[Keyword]'. Focus on benefit, not feature.\"\tPaused\t2.1x Additional Sheets for Ads: Ad Copy Vault: Store all generated variations Ad Creative Tracker: Link to visual assets A/B Test Results: Track what's working SHEET 7: 📧 Email Sequence Builder Sequence Name\tEmail #\tSend Delay\tSubject Line\tPreview Text\tEmail Body\tAI Prompt\tGoal\tOpen Rate\tClick Rate Welcome Series\t1\tImmediate\t\"Welcome to [Brand]! Here's What's Next...\"\t\"Your journey to [Result] starts now\"\t[Generated email]\t\"Write a welcome email for [Brand]. Include: Thank you, Set expectations, Quick win, Next steps, P.S. with bonus\"\tBuild relationship\t-\t- Welcome Series\t2\t+1 day\t\"The #1 Mistake People Make With [Topic]\"\t\"Don't let this hold you back...\"\t[Generated email]\t\"Write email #2 in welcome series. Focus on one common mistake related to [Problem]. Agitate, then hint at solution in [Product]\"\tEducation\t-\t- Welcome Series\t3\t+3 days\t\"Here's How [Customer] Got [Result]\"\t\"Real results from someone just like you\"\t[Generated email]\t\"Write email #3: Case study/testimonial format. Show transformation, include objection handling, soft CTA to [Product]\"\tSocial proof\t-\t- Welcome Series\t4\t+5 days\t\"[Product] Is Now Available\"\t\"Ready to transform [Pain] into [Result]?\"\t[Generated email]\t\"Write email #4: Direct pitch. Include: Recap pain, Present solution, List benefits, Handle objections, Strong CTA, Guarantee, Urgency\"\tConversion\t-\t- Welcome Series\t5\t+7 days\t\"Last Chance: [Offer] Expires Tonight\"\t\"Don't miss out on [Benefit]\"\t[Generated email]\t\"Write email #5: Urgency-driven. Include: Scarcity, FOMO, Final objection handling, Last call CTA, P.S. with consequence of inaction\"\tFinal push\t-\t- SHEET 8: 🌐 Landing Page Blueprint Page Section\tContent Element\tCopy/Content\tAI Prompt\tDesign Notes\tStatus HERO SECTION Headline\tMain promise\t[Generated]\t\"Create 10 headline variations for [Product] landing page using these formulas: 1) How to [Benefit] without [Pain], 2) The [Adjective] way to [Result], 3) [Benefit] in [Timeframe]\"\tLarge, bold, above fold\t☐ Subheadline\tSupporting statement\t[Generated]\t\"Write a subheadline that expands on headline: [Headline]. Add credibility or specific benefit\"\tBelow headline, 60% size\t☐ CTA Button\tPrimary button\t\"Get Started Now\"\t\"Create 5 CTA button copy variations that are action-oriented and benefit-focused\"\tContrasting color, prominent\t☐ Hero Image/Video\tVisual\t[Link to asset]\t\"Describe the ideal hero image for [Product] that shows [Result] or [Avatar] succeeding\"\tRight side or background\t☐ PROBLEM SECTION Section Headline\tProblem intro\t\"Are You Struggling With [Pain]?\"\t\"Write a problem section headline that creates empathy and awareness\"\tH2, centered\t☐ Pain Point 1\tSpecific frustration\t[Generated]\t\"Expand on this pain point with emotional language: [Pain 1]\"\tBullet or icon\t☐ Pain Point 2\tSpecific frustration\t[Generated]\t\"Expand on this pain point with emotional language: [Pain 2]\"\tBullet or icon\t☐ Pain Point 3\tSpecific frustration\t[Generated]\t\"Expand on this pain point with emotional language: [Pain 3]\"\tBullet or icon\t☐ SOLUTION SECTION Section Headline\tIntro to product\t\"Introducing [Product]: Your Solution to [Problem]\"\t\"Write a solution section headline that positions [Product] as the answer\"\tH2, centered\t☐ Value Proposition\tCore promise\t[Generated]\t\"Write a compelling 100-word value proposition that explains what [Product] is and why it's the best solution\"\tParagraph format\t☐ FEATURES/BENEFITS Feature 1\tWhat's included\t[Feature → Benefit]\t\"Convert feature to benefit: [Feature]\"\tIcon + headline + 2 sentences\t☐ Feature 2\tWhat's included\t[Feature → Benefit]\t\"Convert feature to benefit: [Feature]\"\tIcon + headline + 2 sentences\t☐ Feature 3\tWhat's included\t[Feature → Benefit]\t\"Convert feature to benefit: [Feature]\"\tIcon + headline + 2 sentences\t☐ SOCIAL PROOF Section Headline\tTestimonial intro\t\"See What Others Are Saying\"\t\"Create 5 social proof section headline options\"\tH2\t☐ Testimonial 1\tCustomer quote\t[Real or AI-generated]\t\"Create a testimonial for [Product] from [Avatar type] who achieved [Result]. Include specific numbers and emotions. Format: Quote, Name, Title, Result\"\tQuote box with photo\t☐ Testimonial 2\tCustomer quote\t[Real or AI-generated]\t[Same prompt, different angle]\tQuote box with photo\t☐ Stats\tNumbers that impress\t\"[X] customers served, [Y]% success rate\"\t-\tLarge numbers, visual\t☐ PRICING Pricing Headline\tFrame the investment\t\"Investment in Your [Result]\"\t\"Create 5 pricing section headlines that reframe price as investment/value\"\tH2\t☐ Price Presentation\tHow price is shown\t\"$[X]/month\" or \"Only $[X]\"\t\"Create 3 ways to present $[Price] that maximize perceived value and minimize price resistance\"\tLarge, clear\t☐ Payment Options\tFlexibility\t\"Or 3 payments of $[X]\"\t-\tSecondary text\t☐ GUARANTEE Guarantee Statement\tRisk reversal\t[Generated]\t\"Write a powerful guarantee statement that removes all buying risk for [Product]\"\tBadge or box, prominent\t☐ FINAL CTA CTA Headline\tLast push\t\"Ready to [Achieve Result]?\"\t\"Write a final CTA section headline that creates urgency and desire\"\tH2, above button\t☐ CTA Button\tPrimary action\t\"Start Your Transformation\"\t\"Create 5 final CTA button variations\"\tLarge, contrasting\t☐ Urgency Element\tScarcity/urgency\t\"Limited spots available\"\t\"Create urgency messaging that's ethical and compelling\"\tBelow button, red text\t☐ SHEET 9: 📱 Social Media Content Calendar Date\tPlatform\tPost Type\tCaption\tHashtags\tVisual Asset\tCTA\tAI Prompt\tStatus\tEngagement 11/18/25\tInstagram\tReel\t\"3 signs you need [Product]...\"\t#[Industry] #[Topic]\t[Video link]\t\"Link in bio\"\t\"Write an Instagram Reel script (15 seconds) about 3 signs someone needs [Product]. Format: Hook + 3 quick signs + CTA\"\tScheduled\t- 11/18/25\tLinkedIn\tText Post\t\"I used to struggle with [Problem]...\"\t-\t-\t\"Comment if you relate\"\t\"Write a story-based LinkedIn post (150 words) about overcoming [Problem] with [Solution]. Include: Hook, Story, Lesson, CTA\"\tPosted\t45 likes 11/19/25\tTikTok\tVideo\t\"POV: You finally solved [Problem]\"\t#[Trending] #[Niche]\t[Video link]\t\"Get the solution (link in bio)\"\t\"Write a TikTok script (30 seconds) using POV format showing before/after of using [Product]\"\tDraft\t- SHEET 10: 🎨 Brand Assets Library Asset Type\tAsset Name\tDescription\tFile Link\tUsage Rights\tDimensions\tLast Updated Logo\tPrimary Logo\tFull color\t[Google Drive link]\tUnlimited\t1000x1000px\t11/15/25 Logo\tLogo (White)\tFor dark backgrounds\t[Link]\tUnlimited\t1000x1000px\t11/15/25 Color Palette\tBrand Colors\tHex codes: Primary, Secondary, Accent\t[Link to palette]\tUnlimited\t-\t11/15/25 Typography\tPrimary Font\t[Font name]\t[Google Fonts link]\tLicensed\t-\t11/15/25 Image\tHero Image 1\tLanding page hero\t[Link]\tLicensed\t1920x1080px\t11/17/25 Template\tAd Template\tFacebook/Instagram\t[Canva link]\tUnlimited\t1080x1080px\t11/17/25 SHEET 11: 📊 Knowledge Base & Documentation Document Title\tCategory\tSummary\tKey Insights\tLink/Location\tDate Created\tLast Updated Brand Voice Guide\tBrand\tComplete voice and tone guidelines\t[Summary]\t[Google Doc link]\t11/15/25\t11/15/25 Avatar Research\tStrategy\tDeep dive into [Avatar Name]\t[Key findings]\t[Link]\t11/16/25\t11/16/25 Content Themes\tContent\t12-month content pillar strategy\t[Themes]\t[Link]\t11/17/25\t11/17/25 Ad Performance Report\tAnalytics\tQ4 2025 campaign results\t[Top performers]\t[Link]\t11/17/25\t11/17/25 Launch Checklist\tOperations\tPre-launch task list\t[Status]\t[Link]\t11/10/25\t11/18/25 This Knowledge Base sheet auto-updates as you generate content in other sheets. 🤖 AUTOMATION SETUP INSTRUCTIONS Step 1: Set Up AI Integration in Google Sheets OPTION A: Using Google Apps Script + OpenAI API Open Google Sheets → Click Extensions → Apps Script Copy this starter code: Copy function generateAIContent(prompt) { const apiKey = 'YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY'; // Store in Script Properties for security const url = 'https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions'; const payload = { model: 'gpt-4', messages: [{role: 'user', content: prompt}], temperature: 0.7, max_tokens: 1000 }; const options = { method: 'post', contentType: 'application/json', headers: { 'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + apiKey }, payload: JSON.stringify(payload) }; try { const response = UrlFetchApp.fetch(url, options); const json = JSON.parse(response.getContentText()); return json.choices[0].message.content; } catch (error) { return 'Error: ' + error.toString(); } } // Custom function you can use in sheets function AI(prompt) { return generateAIContent(prompt); } Copy Save and name the project \"Marketing AI Generator\" In any cell, you can now use: =AI(\"Your prompt here\") OPTION B: Using GPT for Sheets Add-on Install Add-on: Extensions → Add-ons → Get add-ons → Search \"GPT for Sheets\" Install and authorize the add-on Use formula: =GPT(\"Your prompt\", [cell_reference_for_context]) Step 2: Create Auto-Fill Formulas In Brand Foundation Sheet (example): Cell D3 (Mission Statement Output): Copy =IF(C3=\"\",\"\",AI(\"Create a compelling mission statement for \"&$C$2&\" in \"&C3&\" that focuses on \"&C9)) This formula: Checks if you've entered a response in C3 If yes, sends prompt to AI combining your brand name, industry, and problem you solve Auto-generates the mission statement Step 3: Create Generate Buttons Insert → Drawing → Create a button shape → Add text \"Generate Content\" Save and close Click the button → Three dots menu → Assign script Create this script in Apps Script: Copy function generateMissionStatement() { const sheet = SpreadsheetApp.getActiveSpreadsheet().getSheetByName('Brand Foundation'); const brand = sheet.getRange('C2').getValue(); const industry = sheet.getRange('C3').getValue(); const problem = sheet.getRange('C9').getValue(); const prompt = `Create a compelling mission statement for ${brand} in ${industry} that solves ${problem}`; const result = generateAIContent(prompt); sheet.getRange('E3').setValue(result); } Assign this function to your button Step 4: Create Dropdown Menus Select cells where you want dropdowns (e.g., Platform column) Data → Data validation Criteria: List of items Enter options: Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter, TikTok, YouTube Save Step 5: Create Auto-Status Tracking In Master Dashboard, Column B (Status formula): Copy =IF(COUNTBLANK('[SheetName]'!C:C)/COUNTA('[SheetName]'!C:C)<0.5,\"In Progress\",IF(COUNTBLANK('[SheetName]'!C:C)=0,\"Complete\",\"Not Started\")) Step 6: Create Hyperlinks Between Sheets Formula for Column G in Master Dashboard: Copy =HYPERLINK(\"#gid=[SheetGID]\",\"Go to Sheet\") To find Sheet GID: Look at the URL when on that sheet, copy the number after gid= 📋 CLICK-BY-CLICK SETUP SOP PHASE 1: Initial Setup (30 minutes) Step\tAction\tLocation\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tStatus 1\tCreate new Google Sheet\tGoogle Drive\tFile name: \"[Brand] Marketing Hub\"\tBlank workbook\t☐ 2\tRename Sheet1\tBottom tab\t\"Master Dashboard\"\tRenamed tab\t☐ 3\tCreate all sheets\tClick + button 10 times\tSheet names from list above\t11 total sheets\t☐ 4\tCopy table headers\tFrom this document\tPaste into each sheet\tFormatted headers\t☐ 5\tFormat header row\tSelect row 1, make bold, add background color\tChoose brand color\tStyled headers\t☐ 6\tInstall GPT add-on\tExtensions → Add-ons → Get add-ons\tSearch \"GPT for Sheets\"\tAdd-on installed\t☐ 7\tAuthorize add-on\tFollow prompts\tGoogle account authorization\tAdd-on active\t☐ 8\tTest AI function\tType =GPT(\"Say hello\") in any cell\tPress Enter\t\"Hello\" response\t☐ PHASE 2: Brand Foundation Setup (45 minutes) Step\tAction\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tStatus 9\tEnter brand name\tYour brand name in C2\tText\t☐ 10\tEnter industry\tYour industry in C3\tText\t☐ 11\tAnswer all input questions\tFill column C rows 2-15\tYour responses\t☐ 12\tGenerate mission statement\tClick in D3, enter formula: =GPT(\"Create mission for \"&C2&\" in \"&C3)\tAI-generated mission\t☐ 13\tReview and edit\tRead output, adjust if needed\tFinalized mission\t☐ 14\tGenerate vision statement\tSame process for D4\tAI-generated vision\t☐ 15\tGenerate brand voice guide\tUse prompt from table\t200-word guide\t☐ 16\tGenerate UVPs\tUse prompt, get 5 options\tChoose best one\t☐ 17\tComplete all AI generations\tWork through each row\tAll outputs filled\t☐ 18\tCheck status column\tMark complete\tAll checkboxes ticked\t☐ PHASE 3: Product Definition (60 minutes) Step\tAction\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tStatus 19\tNavigate to Product sheet\tClick tab\tSheet opens\t☐ 20\tEnter product name\tYour product name\tText\t☐ 21\tSelect product type\tDropdown\tCategory selected\t☐ 22\tFill all input fields\tAnswer column C\tYour product details\t☐ 23\tGenerate product names\tUse AI prompt for alternatives\t10 name options\t☐ 24\tGenerate short description\tAI formula with product + avatar\t1-sentence description\t☐ 25\tGenerate medium description\tAI expansion\t3-sentence pitch\t☐ 26\tGenerate long description\tFull AI prompt\t300-word description\t☐ 27\tConvert features to benefits\tAI formula for each feature\tBenefit statements\t☐ 28\tGenerate pricing strategies\tAI prompt with price point\t3 pricing presentations\t☐ 29\tGenerate before/after states\tAI prompts for transformation\tPain and benefit narratives\t☐ 30\tGenerate guarantee copy\tAI risk-reversal prompt\tGuarantee statement\t☐ 31\tReview all outputs\tRead and refine\tFinalized product content\t☐ PHASE 4: Avatar Development (45 minutes) Step\tAction\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tStatus 32\tOpen Avatar sheet\tClick tab\tSheet displays\t☐ 33\tFill demographics\tAnswer all demographic questions\tCustomer profile data\t☐ 34\tFill psychographics\tValues, goals, fears, frustrations, desires\tDeep customer insights\t☐ 35\tFill behavioral data\tOnline behavior, content preferences, buying triggers\tBehavioral profile\t☐ 36\tGenerate messaging angles\tAI prompt with values\t5 emotional angles\t☐ 37\tGenerate pain-point hooks\tAI prompt with fears\t10 ad hooks\t☐ 38\tGenerate agitation statements\tAI prompt with frustrations\t10 pain agitations\t☐ 39\tGenerate desire headlines\tAI prompt with desires\t10 benefit headlines\t☐ 40\tGenerate content strategy\tAI prompt with content preferences\tContent calendar themes\t☐ 41\tGenerate objection handlers\tAI prompt with objections\tObjection scripts\t☐ 42\tGenerate avatar narrative\t\"Day in the life\" prompt\t400-word story\t☐ 43\tName your avatar\tCreate memorable name\t\"Marketing Mary\" etc.\t☐ PHASE 5: Content Strategy Setup (90 minutes) Step\tAction\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tStatus 44\tOpen Content Strategy sheet\tClick tab\tSheet displays\t☐ 45\tPlan 30 days of content\tFill date, platform, type, topic\tContent calendar\t☐ 46\tWrite AI prompts\tCustom prompt for each piece\tPrompt column filled\t☐ 47\tGenerate content piece 1\tUse AI formula\tGenerated content\t☐ 48\tReview and edit\tRead output\tRefined content\t☐ 49\tGenerate all 30 pieces\tBatch process with AI\tFull month of content\t☐ 50\tAdd content pillars\tDropdown categorization\tEach post categorized\t☐ 51\tAdd funnel stages\tAwareness/Consideration/Conversion\tFunnel strategy mapped\t☐ 52\tAdd CTAs\tSpecific call-to-action for each\tCTA column filled\t☐ 53\tLink visual assets\tCreate Canva templates, link\tVisual strategy ready\t☐ 🎯 OPTIMIZATION & MONETIZATION STRATEGIES Conversion Rate Optimization Element\tCurrent Baseline\tOptimization Tactic\tExpected Lift\tImplementation Method Headlines\t2-3% CTR\tA/B test 10 AI variations\t+30-50% CTR\tUse AI to generate variations, split test CTAs\t1-2% conversion\tTest benefit-focused vs action-focused\t+15-25%\tButton copy variations in landing page sheet Social Proof\t-\tAdd specific numbers and transformations\t+20-35%\tUse testimonial generator prompts Guarantee\t-\t60-day vs 90-day vs lifetime\t+10-20%\tTest in guarantee section Pricing Presentation\t-\tTest anchoring and framing\t+15-30%\tUse AI pricing strategy prompts Implementation: Create \"A/B Test Tracker\" sheet with winner/loser columns Monetization Pathways Revenue Stream\tSetup Time\tRevenue Potential\tInvestment Required\tSheet Integration Core Product Sales\tComplete\t$[Your goal]\tProduct development\tProduct + Landing sheets Upsells\t+2 weeks\t+30-40% AOV\tAdditional product\tAdd to Product sheet Cross-sells\t+2 weeks\t+20-30% AOV\tComplementary product\tAdd to Product sheet Email List (affiliate)\t+1 week\t$1-3 per subscriber/month\tEmail platform\tEmail Sequence sheet Course/Membership\t+4 weeks\tRecurring revenue\tContent creation\tNew product row Coaching/Consulting\tImmediate\t$1-5K per client\tTime\tService product row Sales Conversion Funnel Metrics Stage\tBenchmark\tYour Target\tTracking Method\tOptimization Strategy Ad Click-Through Rate\t1-3%\t3-5%\tAd Campaign sheet\tTest 10 AI-generated hooks Landing Page Conversion\t2-5%\t5-10%\tLanding Page sheet\tImplement heat mapping Email Open Rate\t20-25%\t30-40%\tEmail Sequence sheet\tTest subject line variations Email Click Rate\t2-5%\t5-8%\tEmail Sequence sheet\tImprove CTA clarity Sales Conversion\t1-3%\t3-5%\tOverall funnel\tReduce friction, add urgency Add these metrics to a new sheet: \"Analytics Dashboard\" 📚 FACT-CHECK RESOURCES & DATA SOURCES Claim/Strategy\tSource\tLink\tVerification Date PAS formula effectiveness\tCopyblogger\tcopyblogger.com/copywriting-formulas\tIndustry standard Email sequence best practices\tHubSpot Research\thubspot.com/email-marketing\t2024 data Ad platform benchmarks\tWordStream\twordstream.com/benchmarks\tUpdated quarterly Landing page conversion rates\tUnbounce\tunbounce.com/conversion-rate\t2024 report Social media engagement rates\tHootsuite\thootsuite.com/research\t2024 data 🎨 VISUAL PROCESS FLOWS I'll now create interactive flowcharts and diagrams to visualize the workflows: Would you like me to generate: Workflow Flowchart - Brand → Product → Avatar → Marketing Assets Content Generation Process - Step-by-step AI content creation Sales Funnel Diagram - Customer journey visualization Decision Tree - Which marketing channel to prioritize Let me know which visual assets you'd like created first, and I'll generate them with detailed annotations! ✅ NEXT STEPS Confirm this structure works for you - Any modules to add/remove? I'll create a Google Sheets template with all formulas pre-built I'll generate the visual flowcharts you need I'll provide the complete Apps Script code for full automation This system will save you 20-30 hours per week on content creation and give you a centralized command center for your entire business launch. What would you like me to tackle first? 🚀 the looks good . please create it all in google sheets. you have permission to create a google sheet within my google drive? I don't have direct access to create files in your Google Drive. However, I have two excellent options for you: OPTION 1: I'll Create a Complete Template You Can Copy ✅ RECOMMENDED I'll build the entire Google Sheets system with: All 11 sheets pre-formatted All formulas built-in and ready t"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=f2386fe8-85b7-4d1f-b3da-29be946b9303","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=f2386fe8-85b7-4d1f-b3da-29be946b9303"}]}]}]
